Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:05.79,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,如果这样下去说不定能知道雷兹纳的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.79,0:01:08.57,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,无法战斗 请逃离
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:10.20,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,让我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.21,0:01:48.75,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.08,0:01:51.75,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.52,0:01:55.38,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,不 我是说那时候的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.89,0:01:58.70,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,这时候不要说以前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:12.18,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,大家快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.02,0:02:26.64,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,来吧 大家坐那航天飞机回地球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.76,0:02:36.76,Layzner_Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,760)}接下来去地球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.15,0:02:47.85,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,在被摧毁的一点都不剩的联合国基地里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.44,0:02:49.84,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,有八个小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.36,0:02:55.68,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,和好像是伊丽莎白博士的朋友的 美军飞行员存活着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.00,0:03:01.20,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,之前令大家都害怕的无人战斗机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:02.55,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,现在终于不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.11,0:03:09.49,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,可是 还要这样战斗到什么时候呢 真令人不安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.75,0:03:23.36,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白 你会在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.36,0:03:27.93,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,别说了 你快睡吧 现在的你最需要的是睡眠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:38.07,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,怎么办 要马上出发吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:39.14,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,不 现在还不能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:41.30,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,等一下要直接去联合国的宇宙基地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:42.95,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,联合国的宇宙基地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:44.41,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,对 巴西的那一个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:46.89,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,话虽这么说 那为什么不能马上出发呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.89,0:03:48.04,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,要计算轨道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:51.56,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,算好出发时间 并以最短的距离到基地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.07,0:03:55.69,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,可是再这样拖下来 一会那些杀人机器又会回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:58.11,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,还是快逃比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.11,0:04:00.54,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,亚瑟 你还想重蹈覆辙是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:05.06,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,如果胡乱出发的话 别人又会不相信我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.06,0:04:08.08,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,而且地球周边还有很多军事卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:10.33,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我们坐这太空船会被集火攻击的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:12.86,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,会相信我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:16.02,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,只有博士所在的联合国总部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:20.40,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,是哦 仔细想想也没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:24.80,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,其他军队的家伙都是些死脑筋的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:26.37,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,正如西蒙尼所说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:29.17,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我叫安娜 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:29.17,Default_Sub_Top,,0,0,0,,对 这样最安全
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:33.41,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,哈迪 你会说自己的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:37.70,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我叫兰蒂 他是哈迪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.05,0:04:39.22,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,他有点害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:40.75,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我是乔伊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:42.78,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,这孩子叫梅丽莎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.86,0:04:46.80,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,还有罗拉和弗洛华 我是芙蕾蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:50.60,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我是马卡斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:53.51,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我是亚瑟 她是西蒙尼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:55.18,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,请多指教哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:07.95,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,好沉闷的小家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:09.16,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,算出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.36,0:05:11.49,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,以地球时间来算的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.73,0:05:14.02,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,在1小时12分5秒后出发的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:16.94,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,可以刚好到该国首都的上空
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.32,0:05:18.62,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,约一小时是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.37,0:05:22.60,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,为了不要搞错出发时间 已把资料输入电脑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:24.46,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:27.70,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我们能回地球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:30.69,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,对 再过一小时出发的话就能回地球了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.43,0:05:40.00,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,什么嘛 大家都会笑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:42.61,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,目标的坐标位置
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:44.07,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,X-1
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:47.06,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,Y-21 Z-35
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.06,0:05:48.66,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,准备回收监督的船
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:49.76,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.19,0:05:50.78,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.14,0:05:51.68,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.01,0:05:52.74,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:53.59,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.98,0:05:54.51,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,0
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:12.81,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:15.67,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你就是阿尔巴特洛·玖丽亚·飞鸟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.67,0:06:16.08,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:19.07,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你就是那叛徒的姐姐是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:22.83,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我是被派去说服我弟弟的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:24.83,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,说服是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:28.30,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,已经不需要说服他了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:29.13,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:32.73,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我们的计划有点变化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.90,0:06:33.97,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,根据我们的新计划
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.22,0:06:36.89,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,只要能打倒在月球上地球两大强国的基地的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.09,0:06:41.68,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,就能到达地球 并且展开大规模的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:45.25,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,但目前的地球什么事都还没发生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:50.11,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我们决定要直接进入地球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:51.65,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,那英二他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:54.04,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你说古拉多斯人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:56.00,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,还是地球人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:57.93,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我是古拉多斯人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:04.91,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,跟你的弟弟不同 你能为古拉多斯而死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:05.87,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.87,0:07:09.08,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,有这种觉悟啊 是因为知道那件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.08,0:07:09.97,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:11.50,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,就是中尉死掉的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:13.59,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,难道是 盖尔中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.59,0:07:14.99,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,什么 你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:16.62,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:19.90,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,接下来由我告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:21.90,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,杀了盖尔中尉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:23.65,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,就是你的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.85,0:07:31.09,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:32.60,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,再过一小时出发对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:33.04,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:40.94,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:42.83,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:45.28,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你想问这个人的事是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.28,0:07:49.28,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,没错 我们以前有交往过 只是这样的关系而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.58,0:07:50.80,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,是你的恋人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:54.69,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,看不出来你还挺精的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:57.32,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,对不起 我太多事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:08:00.65,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,没关系 如你所说 他曾是我的恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:03.56,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,但那已是以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.32,0:08:23.41,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,再做一下鬼脸嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.45,0:08:28.19,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,那么那叫古雷特的 就是博士以前的男友咯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:30.19,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,好像是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:33.39,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,在战场上和受伤的旧情人再见面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.39,0:08:35.56,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,真浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:38.70,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,如果我受伤的话 你会照顾我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:39.65,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:40.67,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:42.26,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,真 的 呦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.56,0:08:50.86,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,不行 不行 不可以摸那里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:53.65,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,都说不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:57.17,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.25,0:08:59.77,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,好热闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.77,0:09:01.58,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,他很受小孩子欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:08.75,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,明明这么吵的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:10.95,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,他太累了 让他睡一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:12.66,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,接下来 我也
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.66,0:09:13.50,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:15.81,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,不受欢迎的男人不要待在这较好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.19,0:09:18.66,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:19.36,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.91,0:09:28.57,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,罗安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.57,0:09:30.04,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我来跟你换班了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:31.46,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:34.01,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我的生理状态已经到达极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:37.34,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,敌人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:38.67,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,快开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:39.68,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.28,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,杰克 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:43.28,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,快逃 大家快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.28,0:09:45.37,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:46.47,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,约翰 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:47.52,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.80,0:09:51.03,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,这是梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:53.03,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你发烧了 好热
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:55.62,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.62,0:09:57.62,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,醒来反而一片黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:10:00.84,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,就算是噩梦 至少在梦中我还看得到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:02.13,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,伤口不痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:03.71,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,这是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.71,0:10:05.25,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,是外星人的航天飞机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:05.95,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:07.69,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,什么时候能到地球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:09.19,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我们现在还在月球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:11.28,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,还要四十分钟出发
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.89,0:10:13.05,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,让我看一下伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:14.15,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.15,0:10:14.83,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:16.17,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,不要逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:19.51,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,现在的你需要身为医生的我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:20.96,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你好像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.96,0:10:24.25,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,认为那时候的我不需要你是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:26.95,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,如果你这么想就错了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.95,0:10:30.44,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我现在一样需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:31.71,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,但是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:33.71,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,却一直躲着我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:35.62,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,说到这个我也有话要说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:36.66,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.66,0:10:38.66,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,在我最需要你的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.06,0:10:40.26,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你也没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:42.66,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,无论你做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:43.86,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我都希望你回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:46.86,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,就算 是电话的声音也好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.49,0:10:48.70,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,不是才一星期而已吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.93,0:10:50.78,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,对那时的我来说太长了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:56.00,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,别再说了 都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:10:58.70,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,有点化脓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:11:02.38,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,对啊 刚才有点刺痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.38,0:11:04.01,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你也这能忍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:06.09,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我是男子汉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.09,0:11:09.24,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,而且我也有活在黑暗中的觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:13.70,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,这样下去会失明的 他需要药
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:17.21,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,资料信息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.50,0:11:20.47,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,外面有侦测到红外线生命体移动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:23.09,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,方位 右前方5单位处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.31,0:11:25.38,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,无带有敌意的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:27.13,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,雷达关闭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:37.03,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,一起下去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:38.28,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,下去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:40.38,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:43.46,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,男孩子虽然很单纯 但却又很害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.46,0:11:45.46,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,很难说出 喜欢 这个词
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.46,0:11:47.80,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,所以明明喜欢却装得很讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:50.15,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,还会故意恶作剧 故意做出令人讨厌的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.15,0:11:52.25,Default_Sub_Top,,0,0,0,,真拿你们没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.39,0:11:57.45,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,都叫你们住手了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:07.07,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你醒了么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:09.07,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我睡多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:11.62,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我也睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.85,0:12:12.93,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,离出发还有多久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.93,0:12:14.93,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,还有十分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:19.09,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,不好了 博士不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.34,0:12:36.14,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,那么 博士什么都没说就出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:38.34,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,可没想到伊丽莎白她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.35,0:12:40.70,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:47.87,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.11,0:12:49.46,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:50.68,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:52.38,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.38,0:12:54.42,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,罗安 是我 不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:56.59,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,博士 你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:12:59.72,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我现在在地下的医疗中心的前面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.72,0:13:00.68,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,在医疗中心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.72,0:13:03.87,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,对 等我拿完了抗生素
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.87,0:13:06.28,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,马上就回去 别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:08.28,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,叫我们别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:10.14,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,可是十分钟后就要出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.94,0:13:13.47,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,这附近好像没有那种无人杀人机器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:15.11,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,所以拿到东西后只要五分钟就能回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.11,0:13:16.46,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:18.42,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,可恶 都是我的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.42,0:13:18.99,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:20.01,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你在那不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:22.01,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我马上过去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.31,0:13:23.86,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,太帅了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:24.78,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:30.26,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,警告 有十三架TS-SKALLGUNNER-50C入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.34,0:13:31.06,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,敌人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:32.37,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,亚瑟 剩下的拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:33.44,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:39.25,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,980)\bord1\3c&HE5F3CB&\b0}骷髅炮手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.04,0:15:13.96,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.74,0:15:20.09,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,博士 请上来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.39,0:15:29.55,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:33.37,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,第二镜头跟第一镜头处 有四架骷髅炮手快速接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:48.85,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,罗安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:50.85,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,把他们引离航天飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.85,0:15:52.10,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,怎么引开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:53.45,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,直接攻过去 不要怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:02.29,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.03,0:16:20.02,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.02,0:16:21.66,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,把他们引离航天飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:23.08,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.18,0:16:27.47,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,快走开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.78,0:16:40.63,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.63,0:16:41.24,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:35.94,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.44,0:17:39.81,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,离设定的出发时间2.00分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.81,0:17:43.33,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,请雷兹纳 巴鲁迪 贝布鲁尽快回航天飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:45.36,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,罗安 大卫 你们快回航天飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.57,0:17:46.60,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,剩下的我来想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.69,0:17:47.91,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,英二 你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:51.12,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,别说了 快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.12,0:17:52.50,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:15.90,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,大卫 回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.61,0:18:22.85,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你想让博士去送死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.18,0:18:25.71,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我知道了 我回去就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:28.11,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,对不起 都是因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:53.23,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,离设定出发时间还有01:00分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:55.08,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,开始倒数
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.08,0:18:56.00,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,59...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.00,0:18:57.09,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,58...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.09,0:18:58.12,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,57...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,0:18:59.81,Default_Sub_Top,,0,0,0,,56... 55...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.29,0:18:59.04,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,英二
