Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:12.96,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,现状对我方不利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:14.96,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,请快脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:16.41,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,无法战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.41,0:19:17.86,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,请脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:20.67,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,无法战斗 请脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.24,0:19:24.30,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,无法战斗 请脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:26.30,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,搭乘者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.30,0:19:28.62,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,请脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:34.39,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,如果这样下去 说不定能知道雷兹纳的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:42.06,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,38...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.06,0:19:44.06,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,37... 36...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.06,0:19:46.06,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,35... 34...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:47.00,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,33...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:50.74,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,右腕部受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.74,0:19:52.74,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,无法战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.74,0:19:56.03,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,搭乘者请脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.30,0:19:57.25,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,让我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.56,0:20:19.84,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.66,0:20:40.54,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我 什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:45.03,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你是 雷 吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:46.84,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.84,0:21:48.84,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,不是雷 那你到底是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.56,0:21:59.08,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:12.61,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,10... 09...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.61,0:22:14.61,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,08... 07...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.61,0:22:16.61,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,06... 05...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.61,0:22:18.61,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,04... 03...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.61,0:22:20.61,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,02... 01...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.61,0:22:21.92,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,00...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.76,0:22:28.87,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我们离开月球了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.87,0:22:30.87,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,马上就到地球
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.87,0:22:34.71,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,但是 看到那一幕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.71,0:22:36.71,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我却高兴不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.39,0:22:38.71,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:41.68,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,雷兹纳好像被恶魔附身一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.68,0:22:43.87,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,令人毛骨悚然
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.78,0:23:55.69,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,飞鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.10,0:23:58.24,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你知道我父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.90,0:24:00.24,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,这里是欧洲大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.63,0:24:02.24,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,怎么能在这里被干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.90,0:24:04.50,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你还活着吗 盖尔前辈
